visual_description.name: chocolate_cupcake_with_strawberry.jpg
visual_description.description: Chocolate cupcake topped with whipped cream and a fresh strawberry. Slightly uneven cream, natural lighting, visible cupcake liner. Colors are vivid, composition centered, close-up framing. Image slightly grainy.
visual_description.score_basis: The image captures a delicious cupcake, but the focus is a bit soft, and graininess reduces the sharpness. Lighting is natural but uneven. Close-up works but lacks professional sharpness. Vivid colors add appeal.
